TRIPS around the SUN ☀️ 
With all their highs and lows🏔️

INSPIRED as I watch you grow🌻

HAPPY birthday to you sweet friend 🎉

For MANY reasons that I won’t get into It’s been A WHILE since I put music out. A major LIFE moment happened and I was confronted with the infamous “LIFE IS TOO SHORT”. So… with the help of two very trusted members of my chosen family and a LOT of support from many around me and my FAVORITE ANGEL 🦋…..
I share with you CANYON.
This song means SO MUCH to me and I hope that maybe you can find YOUR meaning in it too.

THANK YOU is not enough to @dankalisher for saying yes and helping to make it all more MAGICAL than I could imagine. You are an INSANE one man band. Don’t worry, there’s more.

MY SISTER @shobean, THANK YOU for helping me stay ROOTED in my story. My TRUE voice. 

The TEARS of gratitude that fall from my eyes every time I listen are because of both of you…

WRITTEN by: ME
PRODUCER: @dankalisher
ALL INSTRUMENTS: @dankalisher

Year 2
it still REALLY hurts
But I’m still STANDING
I continue to hear you  in MUSIC
You take WINGS and FLY in nature
In my STILLNESS your voice becomes so clear, always starting with how PROUD you are
I know MA. I know
I’m stronger, it’s def YOUR STRENGTH or maybe it’s OURS now
Friends share with me when you visit them, I laugh and say youre just being nosy 
I laugh
I’m LAUGHING

I miss you in a way that I can’t put into words…

Someone told me: it doesn’t get EASIER, you just get used to it. Well it’s DEFINITELY NOT easier and I’m NOT QUITE used to it, but I made it THROUGH another year

Thank God you’re EVERYWHERE 

love, me
